## Description
This project is a Java console application that calculates
the total marks, average, and grade of a student based on
the marks obtained in three subjects.

## Features
- Accepts student name and marks
- Calculates total and average
- Displays grade using conditional statements
- Simple and user-friendly output

## Technologies Used
- Java
- VS Code

## How to Run
1. Compile the program:
   javac StudentGrade.java
2. Run the program:
   java StudentGrade

